# chezmoi removal allowlist for devcontainer home volume.
#
# IMPORTANT: This is NOT generic drift cleanup. chezmoi only removes
# files explicitly listed here. Files in $HOME that are neither
# managed nor listed here are left alone.
#
# Keep empty on day 1. Add patterns only after:
#   1. Running `chezmoi apply --dry-run --verbose` to preview
#   2. Verifying no seeded essentials (.bashrc, .zshrc, .profile, .ssh)
#      are accidentally matched
#   3. Confirming patterns are NOT also in .chezmoiignore (ignored
#      files are never removed per chezmoi docs — the ignore wins).
#
# Reference: https://www.chezmoi.io/reference/special-files/chezmoiremove/
